{"tid":1475261,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"談與美斯之別 C朗：我曾為不同球隊贏歐聯","createTime":"2019-08-15T12:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T02:07:44.000Z","uid":43785,"like":14,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe09d4d5e8efe2ee03de7fdd1396b7af8e2f5bf","tid":1475261,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6wyfn81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6wyfn81.jpg&h=d30f23f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美斯與基斯坦奴朗拿度過去10年都被視為球壇最強人馬，亦是球迷與媒體比較的對象。對於兩人的分別，C朗直言自己曾為不同球會贏得歐聯冠軍，似是暗示比對方優勝。<br />\n<br />\nC朗先後助曼聯及皇家馬德里贏得歐聯冠軍，在他心目中這似乎是自己比美斯優勝的地方之一，他道：「美斯是十分出色的球員，他不單贏得多次金球獎，而且連續多年都能維持高水平表現，這點跟我一樣。我們不同的地方是，我曾效力不同球會，並也能贏得歐聯。我也連續6年成為歐聯神射手。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8W7PsBi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8W7PsBi.jpg&h=83797356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nC朗去季轉投祖雲達斯，不少人也看好他可以領該意甲班霸登上歐洲之巔，奈何他們在8強意外不敵阿積士出局。（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbgz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=98a49daa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n收皮啦C朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我覺得美斯勁過佢囉"},{"pid":"01ba5d7a5ea9750366a7712c9a8d6b62e2052b2a","tid":1475261,"uid":174432,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Rvab3G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Rvab3G.png&h=48547b11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鳩蛇晚安"},{"pid":"487edae194a5e3b1d0090856067f862195143ca4","tid":1475261,"uid":137688,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fWPVoau.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfWPVoau.png&h=0bf151f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"558b73dcdb3fa8d7b10c32